///---\\\
:GRAPH STATE_OF_WORLD
:TITLE State of the World
:X-DIV 4
:Y-DIV 4
:NO-LEGEND 4
:SCALE
:VAR population
:Y-MIN 0
:Y-MAX 1.2e+10
:DATASET 
:SCALE
:VAR food
:Y-MIN 0
:Y-MAX 6e+12
:DATASET 
:SCALE
:VAR industrial output
:Y-MIN 0
:Y-MAX 4e+12
:DATASET 
:SCALE
:VAR persistent pollution index
:Y-MIN 0
:Y-MAX 40
:DATASET 
:SCALE
:VAR nonrenewable resources
:Y-MIN 0
:Y-MAX 2e+12
:DATASET 

:GRAPH MATERIAL_STANDARD_LIVING
:TITLE Material standard of living
:X-DIV 4
:Y-DIV 4
:NO-LEGEND 4
:SCALE
:VAR food per capita
:Y-MIN 0
:Y-MAX 1000
:DATASET 
:SCALE
:VAR consumed industrial output per capita
:Y-MIN 0
:Y-MAX 250
:DATASET 
